data.description: PRIME pool View location in the highly desired Central Corridor! Tastefully  updated spacious 2-bed, 2-bath townhome with  charming family room that overlooks the beautiful community pool & lush landscaping!! Enjoy Views from inside your unit or from your private covered patio!  The large, open  kitchen features new SS appliances, custom painted cabinets W/ pulls, & recessed lighting W/ a dimmer. Great space to even add a mobile kitchen island! Unit has had full custom paint, new lighting T/O, Ceiling fans, new vinyl plank flooring, new 6 panel doors & hardware, blinds! Charming atrium foyer! Gated community, lushly landscaped, 2-car covered carport. And in a great location with Murphy's Bridle path, dining, shopping and close to the the 51 Expressway! Must see this updated gem!
